'''扁足折额蟹'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Micippa platipes''}}）为[[蜘蛛蟹總科|蜘蛛蟹總科]][[折额蟹属|折额蟹属]]的动物。折额蟹属原屬[[蜘蛛蟹科|蜘蛛蟹科]][[宝石蟹亚科|宝石蟹亚科]]（Mithracinae）<ref name="sms" />，今屬[[宝石蟹科|宝石蟹科]]（Mithracidae <small>MacLeay, 1838</small>）<ref name = "COL">{{cite web|url= http://www.catalogueoflife.org/annual-checklist/2011/search/all/key/micippa/match/1|title= Species 2000 & ITIS Catalogue of Life: 2011 Annual Checklist.|accessdate= 2012-09-24|authors= Bisby F.A., Roskov Y.R., Orrell T.M., Nicolson D., Paglinawan L.E., Bailly N., Kirk P.M., Bourgoin T., Baillargeon G., Ouvrard D. (red.)|year= 2011|publisher= Species 2000|location= Reading, UK.|archive-date= 2019-09-23|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190923000657/http://www.catalogueoflife.org/annual-checklist/2011/search/all/key/micippa/match/1}}</ref><ref name="Grave">{{cite journal|journal=[[Raffles_Bulletin_of_Zoology|Raffles Bulletin of Zoology]] |year=2009 |volume=Suppl. 21 |pages=1–109 |title=A classification of living and fossil genera of decapod crustaceans |first1=Sammy |last1=De Grave |first2=N. Dean |last2=Pentcheff |first3=Shane T. |last3=Ahyong |url=http://rmbr.nus.edu.sg/rbz/biblio/s21/s21rbz1-109.pdf |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606064728/http://rmbr.nus.edu.sg/rbz/biblio/s21/s21rbz1-109.pdf |archivedate=2011-06-06 }}</ref>。其物種體較厚實而圓，足細長，行動遲緩。多數食腐肉。

分布于[[日本|日本]]、广泛分布于印度太平洋区以及[[中国大陆|中国大陆]]的[[西沙群岛|西沙群岛]]（[[永興島|永興島]]<ref name="sms" />）、[[海南岛|海南岛]]等地，生活环境为海水，多生活于潮间带至20米深的海滨。其生存的海拔下限为-20米。<ref name='id11584'/>

